-- Istanbul Bomb Kills Four on Army Shuttle Bus in First Attack in Two Years
-- Mark Bentley
-- 2010-06-22T05:14:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/three-killed-as-explosion-rocks-army-bus-in-istanbul-cnn-turk-reports.html

          
          
             Three people died after a blast hit
a bus carrying military personnel in the Istanbul suburb of
Halkali today, CNN Turk television reported.  
          
          


  


        